and we'll wait for all those effects to 
completely washout and then we'll be

00:03:57.809 --> 00:03:59.109
testing their

00:03:59.109 --> 00:04:01.839
Parkinson's with a rating scale that's used, 

00:04:01.839 --> 00:04:04.430
and that will be the basis of the data collection for the study.

00:04:05.629 --> 00:04:06.700
As for Dale...

00:04:06.700 --> 00:04:12.440
After his first programming...I can tell you that my trembling has diminished a bit

00:04:12.440 --> 00:04:13.219
with no meds.

00:04:13.219 --> 00:04:15.110
But he understands that it will be

00:04:15.110 --> 00:04:19.239
years before researchers now if DBS
will slow his Parkinson's progression.

